        "id": 5045
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-12-07T15:53:47Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Think it makes sense to promote this up to a private SkCanvas method?  It might help keep people using this if we define it near and make it read like one of the existing quickReject() family.",
